revision.text: symbol A written proper name such as “OBI”; a serial number such as “12324X”; a stop sign. An information content entity that is a mark or character used as a conventional representation of another entity. Une entité support d'information utilisée comme représentation conventionnelle d'une autre entité. 20091104, MC: this needs work and will most probably change Jean-Marc Meunier PERSON: Jonathan Rees based on Oxford English Dictionary is a subclass from http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000030
